# 27.12.2025: Maharashtra Lok Bhavan offers tributes to Dr Panjabrao Deshmukh

**Publish Date :December 27, 2025**

---

Maharashtra Lok Bhavan offers tributes to Dr Panjabrao Deshmukh

Floral tributes were offered to the portrait of former Union Agriculture Minister Dr Panjabrao Deshmukh on his birth anniversary at Maharashtra Lok Bhavan, Mumbai on Saturday (27th  Dec).

Secretary to the  Governor  Dr  Prashant  Narnaware, ADC to the Governor Abhaysinha Deshmukh officers and staff of Maharashtra Lok Bhavan paid tributes to late Dr Panjabrao Deshmukh on the occasion.
